# Input

```html
{ count, plural,
    =0 {{ sex, select,
      other {<p>deeply nested</p>}
    }}
    =other {a lot}
}

{ count123, plural,
  =0 {{ sex, select,
    other {<p>deeply nested</p>}
  }}
  =other {a lot}
}

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,6 +1,9 @@
-{count, plural, =0 {{sex, select, other {<p>deeply nested</p>}}} =other {a lot}}
-
-{count123, plural,
-  =0 {{sex, select, other {<p>deeply nested</p>}}}
-  =other {a lot}
-}
+{ count, plural, =0
+{{ sex, select,
+      other {<p>deeply nested</p>}
+    }}
+=other { a lot} } { count123, plural, =0
+{{ sex, select,
+    other {<p>deeply nested</p>}
+  }}
+=other { a lot} }
```

# Output

```html
{ count, plural, =0
{{ sex, select,
      other {<p>deeply nested</p>}
    }}
=other { a lot} } { count123, plural, =0
{{ sex, select,
    other {<p>deeply nested</p>}
  }}
=other { a lot} }
```

